    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just being tired though. it feels more like... a finality. like i've finished the book and there's no point in reading the same pages over and over. the world just feels so loud and empty at the same time. i keep looking at the horizon and thinking about how peaceful it would be to just stop being a traveler and just... be done with the journey. does that make sense?",
